      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Security and Reliability"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Steward roles must be reflected in access control: a steward cannot fulfill their responsibilities without read access to data quality dashboards, lineage graphs, and the AI asset registry. However, stewards should not automatically receive write access to underlying production datasets — that privilege belongs to the data engineers responsible for remediation. Stewards approve changes; engineers execute them. This separation of duties reduces the risk of accidental or unauthorized data modification."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "For regulatory audits, steward assignment records must be immutable. Use append-only audit logs in the data catalog: record who was assigned as steward, when, by whom, and what decisions they made. Never delete historical steward assignments — a record that a role was vacant during an incident is itself compliance evidence."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "horizontalRule"
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Key Takeaways"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Data stewards are named practitioners, not teams or committees — accountability must resolve to one person."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "GenAI systems require a new steward role — AI/ML Data Steward — to cover prompt libraries, RAG corpora, and training datasets."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "The RACI model (Responsible, Accountable, Consulted, Informed) is the standard tool for making steward assignments explicit and audit-ready."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Stewardship only works when stewards have system access, tooling, and authority — not just a title in a policy document."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Register all steward assignments in the data catalog with effective dates, review cadences, and escalation paths."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Connect steward review completion to AI model deployment gates to prevent ungoverned models reaching production."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Scale stewardship with automated asset discovery, default role assignments by domain, and Steward Councils for related domains."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
